quran[903]{c,v,t}:
  17,1,"Senayee wondanii On Royru…óo Jeyaa…óo Makko on jemma, iwde ka juulirde hormante haa ka juulirde wo…ó…óitiinde, nden nde Men Barkini ban≈ãe mun,fii yo Men Hollu mo immorde e Aayeeje Amen. Pellet, Ko Kanko woni Nanoowo, Yi‚Äôoowo. @Corrected"
  17,2,"Men Jonniino Muusaa Deftere nden, Men Wa…ói nde peewal, wonannde …ìi…ó…ìe Israa‚Äôiila …ìen, wonnde : \"Wata on jogito gaanin Am hooloraa…óo"
  17,3,"[Ko onon yo] …ìi…ó…ìe …ìen …ìe Men wa…ó…óinnoo wonndude e Nuuhu.Pellet, o laatino jeyaa…óo yettoowo"
  17,4,"Men wahyiniino e …ìi…ó…ìe Israa‚Äôiila …ìen ka Deftere [wonnde] : \"On bonnayay ka leydi laabi …ói…ói, on townitoyto kadi townitaare mawnunde"
  17,5,"Si fodoore gootel e …óin …ói…ói arii, Men wurtay e mon jeyaa…ìe Amen, mar…ìe doole tii…óu…óe, …ìe yiiloo hakkunde galleeji …óin. ∆äum wonii fodoore huuwoyteende =golloteende"
  17,6,"Refti Men ruttitanani on doole …óen e hoore ma…ì…ìe; Men ∆Åeydi on jawle e …ìi…ó…ìe,Men Wa…óa on gorol …ìurngol …óuu…óude"
  17,7,"Si on mo∆¥∆¥inii, ko ko'e mon mo∆¥∆¥inan…óon ; si on bonnii kadi, ko ko‚Äôe mon [bonnann…óon]. Si fodoore sakkitiinde nden arii, ko fii yo …ìe hoynu geece mon …óen, e fii yo no …ìe naatiraa ka juulirde wano …ìe naatirnoo e mayre ka laawol aranol, e fii yo …ìe muncu yeru woo ko …ìe townani muncudee"
  17,8,"Hino jortaa ka Joomi mon yurmee on.Si on fillitike (non),Men fillitoo. Men wa…óanii yeddu…ìe …ìen Jahannama on tonngorde"
  17,9,"Pellet, ndee Alqur‚Äôaanaare no fewnay e ko …ìuri e nun…óude,hinde wewlinira=weltanira gom…óim…ìe,…ìen golloo…ìe mo∆¥∆¥u…ói …óin, wonnde, no woodani …ìe njo…ìdi mawndi"
  17,10,"E wonnde pellet, …ìen …ìe gom…óinaa laakara on, Men maranii …ìe lepte muusu…óe"
  17,11,"Ne…ó…óo no toroo bone, wano o tororta non mo∆¥∆¥ere,ne…ó…óanke on wonii ko he√±ii…óo"
  17,12,"Men wa…óii jemma on e √±alorma on Aayeeje …ói…ói, Men monti Aaya jemma on, Men wa…ói Aaya √±alorma on hentii…óo, fii yo on …óa…ì…ìu …ìural immorde ka Joomi mon, e fii yo on anndu limoore duu…ìi, e hasboore. Kala huunde, Men fensitirii nde fensitudee"
  17,13,"Kala ne…ó…óanke, Men wa…ó…óinii mo talkuru makko ndun ka daande makko. Men yaltinanoyay mo √ëalnde Darngal, deftere, o hawra e mayre ko nde fontaande"
  17,14,"Janngu deftere maa nden, hoore-maa yonante hannde hasboowo"
  17,15,"Mo feewii, haray pellet, ko hoore-makko o feewani ; mo majii kadi, haray pellet, ko o majji kon yantay e hoore-makko. Wonkii ronndotaako bone wokki goo. Men wonaali leptoo…ìe, haa Men immina Nulaa…óo"
  17,16,"Si Men faandike halkude saare, Men yamiray neeminaa…ìe mayre …ìen, …ìe faasinqinoo e mayre, konngol (lepte) ngol jojja e mayre, Men munca nde muncudee"
  17,17,"Heewii gire …óe Men halki …ìaawo Nuuhu! Joomi maa Yonii Humpitii…óo, Yi‚Äôoowo junuubi=bakkatuuji jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen"
  17,18,"On taw…óo no faandii yaccinaneede=yaawnaneede, Men yaccinanay mo ton huunde ko Men muuyi, wonannde on mo Men yi…ói, refti Men wa…óana mo Jahannama, o naatoya nge ko o ≈ãi√±aa…óo, pottinaa…óo [yurmeende]"
  17,19,"On faalaa…óo laakara, o gollani ngal golle maggal, hara kanko ko o gom…óin…óo ;…ìen …óon, golle ma…ì…ìe …óen wonii jaarnaa…óe"
  17,20,"Kala (ma…ì…ìe),Me…óen …ìeydana ; …ìee …óoo e …ìee …óoo, immorde e dokkal Joomi maa. Dokkal Joomi maa ngal wonaali ha…óaa ngal"
  17,21,"Ndaarii no Men …ìurniri yoga ma…ì…ìe e dow yoga, ko laakara on …ìuri mawnude darjaaji,…ìuri mawnude kadi …ìural"
  17,22,Wata a wa…óidan Alla rewetee…óo goo ; joo…óoyo…óaa ko a ≈ãi√±aa…óo woppaa…óo
  17,23,"Joomi maa yamirii :\"Wata on rewu ko wanaa Kanko, jibim…ìe …ìen,mo∆¥∆¥agol [e ma…ì…ìe]:si nayewu go…ó…óo e ma…ì…ìe yottike ma,maa …óum …ìe …ói…óo non;wata a wi‚Äôan …ìe \"bis=uf!\" wata a wikko …ìe =wota a furo,wowlan …ìe konngol teddungol"
  17,24,"Yankinano…óaa …ìe yurme…óaa …ìe, wi‚Äôaa: ¬´ Joomi an, yurme …ìe‚Äôe, wano …ìe ne‚Äôirnoo lan non hari ko mi tosokun ¬ª"
  17,25,"Joomi mo'on no Anndi ko woni ka nder wonkiiji mon, si tawii on wonuno mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe ; pellet Kanko O wonanii ruttotoo…ìe …ìen Surroowo"
  17,26,"Jonnu jom …ìadondiral haqqee makko on, e …ìillii…óo, e seteejo haqqee makko on ; wata a funsu funsudee"
  17,27,"Pellet funsoo…ìe …ìen, ko si…ó…ìe seytanuuji …óin ; seytaane non wonii yeddu…óo Joomi mun"
  17,28,"Si a …óurnike …ìe fii …óa…ì…ìugol yurmeende immorde ka Joomi maa, nde jorti…óaa …óum, wi'an …ìe konngol newiingol"
  17,29,"Wata a wa…óu junngo maa ngon ko lmbaango, ka daande maa ; wata a fontu ngo kadi kala fontugol, haa joo…óo…óaa ko a felnii…óo, ninsu…óo"
  17,30,"Pellet Joomi maa, no yan√±ana arsike, on Mo O muuyi. O …ìittina. Pellet Kanko O wonii Humpitii…óo, Yi‚Äôoowo jeyaa…ìe Makko"
  17,31,"Wota on warir …ìi…ì…ìe mon …ìen kulol …ìilla=baasal, ko Menen arsikata …ìe, wonndude e mon ; pellet warugol …ìe ngol, wonii goopol manngol"
  17,32,"Wota on …ìatto jeeno ngon=fijrde nde, pellet …óun wonii pankare e laawol bonungol"
  17,33,"Wata on waru wonkii, ki Allah harmini kin [warugol], si wonaa sabu hakkee. Mo too√±aama waraama, Men wa…óanii heftu…ìe e makko …ìen doole wota non o fantin ka warugol. Pellet Kanko o wonii wallaa…óo"
  17,34,"Wata on …ìatto jawle Alyatiim, si wonaa …ìattagol …ìurngol mo∆¥∆¥ude, haa sagatalaaku makko timma ; humnee aadi ndin; pellet, aadi ndin wonii lannditoytee ndi"
  17,35,"Hunnee …ìetu ngun si on etay, manndikiron manndakke=peeson peese feewu…óe, ko …óun mo∆¥∆¥i, ko ka√±un …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude battane"
  17,36,"Wata a naatu e ko a anndaa fii mun. Pellet nan…óe …óen, e gii…óe …óen e …ìernde nden, …óii…óoo fow wonii lannditoytee…ói ka Makko"
  17,37,"Wata a yaaru ka leydi √±aa∆¥a bunnga, ko fii pellet an a yulataa leydi ndin, a yottotaako pelle …óen junndi=njuuteendi"
  17,38,"…óin fow, bone majji on wonii a√±aa…óun ka Joomi maa"
  17,39,"∆äun, ko go…ó…óun e ko Joomi maa…óa wahayini faade e maa, immorde e √ëee√±al wata a wa…óu rewetee…óo goo wonndude e Alla, sakko werle…óaa ka nder jahannama ko a felaa…óo ra…óaa…óo"
  17,40,"E hara Joomi mon su…ìani on …ìi…ì…ìe wor…ìe, O jogitoo immorde e malaa'ika…ìe …ìen rew…ìe? Pellet, onon hi…óin wowlude konngol mawnungol"
  17,41,"Gom…óii Men fensitii e nder ndee Alqur'aanaare fii yo …ìe waajitor, …óum …ìeydaali …ìe si wonaa wo…ó…óitagol"
  17,42,"Maaku : ¬´ Si tawno no wonndi e makko, rewetee…ói wano …ìe wi‚Äôiri non awa …ói …óa…ì…ìayno laawol ummaade Jom Arsi o.\" @Corrected"
  17,43,"Senayee wonanii Mo, O Toowii gaayi e ko …ìe wi'ata Toowal Mawnungal"
  17,44,"No subunhinannde Mo kammuuli …óin jee…ói…ói e leydi ndin e …ìen wonu…ìe e majji, alaa e hay e huunde si wanaa hinde Subunhinaade sabu Yettugol Mo, kono on faamataa subunhinaali ma…ì…ìe …óin, pellet, Kanko O wonii Mun√±ii…óo Surroowo"
  17,45,Si a janngii Alqur'aanaare nden Men wa…óay hakkonde maa e …ìen …ìe gom…óinaa laahara on heedo suu…óiingo
  17,46,"Men wa…ói e dow …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen cokoo…óe fii wata …ìe faamu nde [Alqur'aanaare nden] e ka noppi ma…ì…ìe kadi teddeele, si a jantike Joomi maa…óa ka nder Alqur'aanaare Kanko Tun …ìe huccinay …ìabbe ma…ì…ìe …óen ko …ìe dogoo…ìe"
  17,47,"Ko Menen Anndi ko …ìe he…óotoo kon, tuma …ìe he…óotoo faade e maa…óa [yo Nulaa…óo], e tuma …ìe sowndondirta=ndeeydata, tuma nde too√±oo…ìe …ìen wi'ata: ¬´On jokkaali si wanaa gorko mbil…óaa…óo=bilaado¬ª"
  17,48,"Ndaarii [yo Nulaa…óo] ko honno …ìe piyiranay maa mise=yeruuji, …ìe majjii …ìe hattantaake [he…ìude] laawol"
  17,49,"∆Åe wi'i: ¬´E hara si men wonii ∆¥i'e e mbu…óu, haray ko men immintinoytee…ìe tagu hesu?¬ª"
  17,50,"Maaku: [yo Nulaa…óo] ¬´Wonee kaa∆¥e maa jam…óe¬ª"
  17,51,"Maa…óun tagu tawayngu no mawni ka …ìer…óe mon, aray …ìe wi'a: 'Ko hommbo ruttata men?\" Maaku: \"Ko On Tagu…óo on ka laawol aranol\". Aray …ìe dimmba ko'e ma…ì…ìe …óen faande e maa, …ìe wi'a: \"∆äun ko honnde tuma\", Maaku: 'No tijjaa nde tawata …ìadike"
  17,52,"√ëannde O noddata on nooto…óon yetton Mo sikkon on √±ii…ìaano [ka leydi] si wanaa see…óa"
  17,53,"Maakan jeyaa…ìe an …ìen: \"Yo …ìe wowlu nden huunde …ìurnde mo∆¥∆¥ude, pellet, Seytaane o bonnay hakkunde ma…ì…ìe, pellet, Seytaane wonanii ne…ó…óanke ga√±o …ìanngu…óo"
  17,54,"Joomi mon ko O Anndu…óo fii mon, si O yi…óii O hinnoo on, maa…óun si O yi…óii O lepta on. Men nulaali ma e dow ma…ì…ìe fawtii…óo"
  17,55,"Ko Joomi maa Annde fii …ìen wom…ìe ka kammuuli e ka leydi, pellet, Men …ìurnii wo…ì…ìe e Annabaa…ìe …ìen e dow wo…ì…ìe, Men Jonni Daawuuda Jabuura"
  17,56,"Maaku: \"Noddee …ìen …ìe aa∆¥i…óon [ko rewetee…ìe] gaanin Makko, …ìe maraa huncugol lorra kan gaayi mo'on wonaa waylugol kadi"
  17,57,"∆Åen, …ìe …ìe woni noddude, hi…ìe …óa…ì…ìude …óoworgal faade e Joomi ma…ì…ìe, ko hommbo e ma…ì…ìe …ìuri …ìadaade, hi…ìe jortii Hinnayee Makko on hi…ìe huli lepte Makko …óen, pellet, lepte Joomi maa …óen …óe laatike ko rentaa…óe"
  17,58,"Alaa e saare si wanaa Menen ko Men halkay…ìe nde ko adii √±alde darngal, maa ko Men leptay…ìe nde lepte sattu…óe, …óun …óon wonii ko winndaa …óun ka Deftere"
  17,59,"Ha…óaali Men nde Men nula Aayeeje …óen, si wanaa sabu fenniino …óe adii…ìe …ìen, Men okki Samuuda Naaqaawa mban yi'teemba …ìe too√±i mba, Men nuliraali Aayeeje …óen si wonaa hul…ìinir…óe"
  17,60,"[Janto] Tuma nde Men wi'anno maa: \"Pellet, Joomi maa O hu…ìindike yim…ìe …ìen, Men wa…óiraali nden yi'annde nde Men hollumaa si wanaa fitina wonannde yim…ìe …ìen e lekki hu…óaaki ki ka Alqur'aana, Me…óen hul…ìina …ìe kono …ìeydataa …ìe si wanaa bewre mawnde"
  17,61,"Nde Men Daalannoo Malaa'ikaa…ìe …ìen sujjanee Aadama, …ìe sujji si wanaa Ibliisa o wi'i: \"Hara mi sujjanay on mo tagu∆äaa e loopal"
  17,62,"O wi'i: \"A yi'ii oo mo teddin∆äaa e dow an, pellet, si A nennanii lan haa √±alde darngal mi bonnay …ìi…ì…ìe makko …ìen si wanaa see…óaa…ìe"
  17,63,"[Alla] Daali: \"Yahu, kala jokku…óo ma e ma…ì…ìe pellet, ko jahannama woni njoddi mon, njoddi yonoori"
  17,64,"Dillinir on mo hattana…óaa e ma…ì…ìe hito maa ngon, poo…óu e dow ma…ì…ìe pucci maa e seppoo…ìe maa, ka fidu e ma…ì…ìe ka jawle e ka …ìi…ì…ìe fodu…ìe, [kono] Seytaane fodaali …ìe si wanaa hodo"
  17,65,"Pellet, Jeyaa…ìe An …ìen a maraa doole e hoore ma…ì…ìe, Joomi maa yonii Hooloraa…óo"
  17,66,"Ko Joomi mon woni sogganay…óo on laa…óe …óen ka maayo, fii yo on …óa…ì…ìu immorde e …ìural Makko ngal, pellet, Kanko ko O Yurmetee…óo on"
  17,67,"Si lorra kan he…ìii on ka maayo, majjay …ìen …ìe noddayno …óon, si wonaa Kanko [Alla] nde O danndi on ka njorndi …óurno…óon, ne…ó…óanke on wonii te o seeraani wonde heewu…óo yeddugol"
  17,68,"Enee, on hooli O mutintaa on ka ban≈ãe njorndi maa…óun O nula e mon damagariire [to…ìo koccu], refti hara he…ìantaake on fawtii…óo"
  17,69,"Kaa on hooli O ruttaraa on e maggo laawol goo O accita e dow mon bippooru immorde e keneeli O yoolira on sabu ko yedduno…óon kon, refti on he…ìantaake jokkitiray…óo e dow amen cukkoowo"
  17,70,"Gom…óii, Men teddinii …ìi…ó…ìe Aadama …ìen, Men ronndike …ìe ka njorndi e ka maayo Men arsiki …ìe immorde e laa…ìu…ói Men …ìurni …ìe e dow ko heewi e …ìen …ìe Men tagi …ìurnudee"
  17,71,"√ëannde Men noddiroyta kala yim…ìe yeesoojo ma…ì…ìe on,kala on jonnitiroyaa…óo deftere makko nden ka √±aamo makko …ìen …óon …ìe janngay deftere ma…ì…ìe nden …ìe too√±irtaake hay yeru gaarayol hun tamaro"
  17,72,"Kala on wonu…óo e [ngurndan aduna] ko o bun…óo, haray kanko, ko ka laahara o …ìurata wumude e majjude laawol"
  17,73,"Fii kala …ìe e…ì…ìii nde …ìe fitinaymaa gaayi nden huunde nde Men wahayini e maa…óa fii yo a fefindo e Amen ko wonaa …óun [ko Men tellini e maa] ontuma …ìe jogitoto ma sehlaajo"
  17,74,"Si tawiino Men tabintinaanoma, gom…óii hari a do'ii oo√±aade e ma…ì…ìe huunde see…óaare"
  17,75,"Ontuma Men mee…óinteno cowale [lepte] ka ngurndan e cowale [lepte] ka mayde refti he…ìantaake ma ballo e hoore Amen"
  17,76,"Fii kala …ìe e…ì…ìiino dillinngol ma ka leydi fii yo …ìe yaltine e mayri, ontuma …ìe √±ii…ìataano …ìatte maa si wanaa see…óa"
  17,77,"∆äun ko Sunna …ìen …ìe Men nuli ko adimaa immorde e Nulaa…ìe Amen, a he…ìantaa Sunna Amen on mbattiigu"
  17,78,"√ëinnu julde nden ka mortagol naange ngen haa ka niwre jemma, Julde subaha nden, pellet, Julde subaha nden wonii seedeteende"
  17,79,"Ka jemma tinno e makko ko …ìeydaari maa…óa, no jortaa nde Joomi maa…óa immintinay maa e darorde yettiniinde"
  17,80,"Maaku: \"Jooma, naadiran naatirgal goonga yaltiniraa mi yaltirgal goonga, wa…óanaa mi immorde ka Maa…óa doole ballal"
  17,81,"Maaku: \"goonga kan arii meere nden fuuyii, pellet, meere nden wonii fuuyoore"
  17,82,"Me…óen tellina ka Alqur'aana huunde nde konde cellal e yurmeende wonnande gom…óin…ìe …ìen, …ìeydataa too√±oo…ìe …ìen si wanaa hayrere"
  17,83,"Si Men neeminii e ne…ó…óanke on o …óuurnoo o townaa balaaje makko, si bone he…ìii mo o wona hattu…óo e ta∆¥ii…óo"
  17,84,"Maaku: \"Mo kala yo gollu e laawol mun, ko Joomi mon woni Anndu…óo on …ìur…óo feewude laawol"
  17,85,"Hi…ìe lanndo maa fii fittaandu, maaku: \"Fittaandu ndun ko e fiyaake Joomi an, on okkaaka e ganndal si wanaa see…óa√©"
  17,86,"Mi woondii, si Me…óen yi…óunoo Men na…ìayno nden huunde nde Men wahyini faade e Maa…óa, refti he…ìantaake ma fawtii…óo …óun e hoore Amen"
  17,87,"Ko woni tun, ko Hinnayee immorde ka Joomi maa, pellet, …ìural Makko ngal e dow maa wonii mawnungal"
  17,88,"Maaku: \"Mi woondii, si yim…ìe …ìen e jinnaaji …óin hawtitii fii yo …ìe addu yeru ndee Alqur'aanaare, …ìe addataa yeru mayre, hay si wonii wo…ì…ìe ma…ì…ìe ko wallindray…ìe e wo…ì…ìe"
  17,89,"Gom…óii Men …ìannginanii yim…ìe …ìen e ndee Alqur'aanaare immorde e kala misal, …ìur…ìe …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen salii, si wanaa yeddugol"
  17,90,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Men gom…óintaa ma, haa …ìullitanaa men ka leydi …ìunndu"
  17,91,Maa…óun laatano maa ngesa immorde e tamorooje e inabuuje …ìullitaa can…ói …óin hakkunde majje …ìullitugol
  17,92,"Maa…óun li…ìaa kammu ngun e hoore amen wano aa∆¥or…óaa non kunte, maa…óun addaa Alla e Maalaa'ikaa…ìe …ìen [men] tiindondira"
  17,93,"Maa…óun laatano maa suudu immorde e cu…óaaje [kan≈ãe], maa…óun ∆¥awaa ka kammu, men gom…óintaa ∆¥awugol maa…óa ngol haa jippinaa e amen deftere men jannga nde. Maaku: \"Senaade Jom an, hara mi wonu, ko wonaa …ìanndinke Nulaa…óo"
  17,94,"Ha…óaali yim…ìe …ìen nde …ìe gom…óinta tuma nde peewalngal arunoo …ìe, si wanaa fii …ìe wi'ii: \"E hara Alla nulay …ìanndinke Nulaa…óo"
  17,95,"Maaku: \"Si tawiino laatinoke ka leydi Malaa'ikaa…ìe hi…ìe yaha ko …ìe deewu…ìe, Men jippinayno e ma…ì…ìe immorde ka kammu Malaa'ikaajo Nulaa…óo"
  17,96,"Maaku: \"Alla yonii Seedii…óo hakkunde an e mon, pellet Kanko O wonii Humpitii…óo Reenu…óo jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen"
  17,97,"On mo Alla fewni ko on woni feewu…óo, …ìe O majjini …ìen a he…ìantaa…ìe walloo…ìe ko woori Mo. Men moo…ìay …ìe √±alde darngal e dow geece ma…ì…ìe …óen ko …ìe wumu…ìe e mbobi…óu= fahdube …ìe e faa…óu…ìe, werde ma…ì…ìe nden ko jahannama tuma kala nge rocci Men …ìeydana …ìe hu…ì…ìunge"
  17,98,"∆äun ko njoddi ma…ì…ìe, sabu kam…ìe …ìe yeddii Aayeeje Amen …óen, …ìe wi'i: \"E hay si men wonii ∆¥i'e e mbu…óu e hara menen ko men immintintee…ìe tagu hesu"
  17,99,"Enee, …ìee yi'aali, wonnde Alla On Tagu…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin ko O Hattan…óo nde O tagata yeru ma…ì…ìe, O wa…óani …ìe lajal [caate] sikke alaa e maggal. Too√±oo…ìe …ìen salii si wanaa yeddugol"
  17,100,"Maaku: \"Sinndo onon hi…óon marunoo ngaluuji Hinnayee Joomi an on, ontuma, on jogitotono kulol nafkugol, ne…ó…óanke on wonii nguddo"
  17,101,"Gom…óii Men okkiino Muusaa Aayeeje jeenay …ìanngu…óe, lanndii …ìi…ì…ìe Israa'iila …ìen tuma nde o arunoo …ìe Fir'awna wi'ani mo: \"Min dey mi…óo sikkumaa ko an yo Muusaa ko a mbil…óaa…óo"
  17,102,"Maaku: \"Go…óii hi…óa anndi jippinaali …óee si wanaa Jey…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin Aayeeje [yi'etee…ói]. Min dey mi…óo sikkumaa ko an yo Fir'awna ko a halkii…óo"
  17,103,O faalaa nde o dillinta …ìe ka leydi Men yooli mo e …ìen wonndu…ìe e makko …ìe denndaangal
  17,104,"Men Daalani …ìaawo makko …ìi…ì…ìe Israa'iila …ìen: \"Ho…óee ka leydi, si fodoore sakkitiinde nden arii, Men adday on ko on muu…ìii…ìe=fiiliibe"
  17,105,"Ko sabu Goonga Men telliniri nde, ko sabu Goonga nde tellii, Men nuliraali ma si wanaa [ko a] wewlinoowo=beltinoowo e jertinoowo"
