  24,1,"Simoore, Men jippinii nde Men farlii nde, Men jippini e nder mayre Aayeeje …ìanngu…óe belajo'o onon on waajitoto"
  24,2,"Debbo jinoowo on e gorko jeenoowo on foccee gooto kala e ma…ì…ìe paatawol(looci) teemedere, wata yurmeende ma…ì…ìe nanngu on e fii Diina Alla kan, si tawii on laatike hi…óon gom…óini Alla e √ëalaande Laakara nden. Yo seedo foccugol …ìe ngol jamaa immorde e gom…óin…ìe …ìen"
  24,3,"Gorko jinoowo on o resataa si wonaa debbo jeenoowo maa…óum sirkoowo, debbo jinoowo on resatah mo si wanaa gorko jinoowo maa…óum sirkoowo, …óum harminaama e dow gom…óin…ìe …ìen"
  24,4,"E …ìen …ìe no tukka rew…ìe sa≈ãii…ìe …ìen refti hara …ìe addaali seedee…ìe nayo, haray piyee …ìe paatawol(looci) cappan…óe jeetati. Wata on ja…ìan …ìe seedagol poomaa. ∆Åen …óon, ko kam…ìe woni Faasiqii…ìe …ìen"
  24,5,"Si wanaa …ìen tuubu…ìe …ìaawo …óum …ìe mo∆¥∆¥ini. Pellet, Alla ko O Surroowo Yurmetee…óo"
  24,6,"E …ìen …ìe no tukka sonnaa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen hara laatanaaki …ìe seedee…ìe si wanaa wonkiiji ma…ì…ìe …óin, ko yo go…ó…óo e ma…ì…ìe seedo seedeeji nayi [o woondira] Alla pellet, kanko ko e goongu…ìe …ìen o jeyaa"
  24,7,"Jowa…ìun …óum, wonndema yo kuddi Alla wonu e dow makko si o laatike jeyaa…óo e fenoo…ìe …ìen"
  24,8,"∆Åe dunyira e [sonnaajo on] lepte …óen, nde o seedotoo seedeeji nayi [o woondira] Alla, pellet [gorko on] ko e fenoo…ìe …ìen o jeyaa"
  24,9,"Jowa…ìun …óum, ko nde Alla tikkata e dow makko si [gorko on] laatike ko e goongu…ìe …ìen o jeyaa"
  24,10,"Sinndo wanaano ∆Åural Alla ngal e dow moo…óon e Yurmeende Makko nden, e wonndema Alla ko O ja…ìoowo tuubuubuye √ëee√±u…óo"
  24,11,"Pellet, …ìen addu…ìe penaale …óen ko …ìe jamaa jeyaa…óo e moo…óon, wata on sikku …óum ko bone mo'on; ko woni …óum ko mo∆¥∆¥ere mo'on. No woodani kala ne…ó…óo immorde e ma…ì…ìe ko o faggitii kon e junuubu, on fawtii…óo maw…óum [junuubu on] immorde e ma…ì…ìe, no woodani mo Lepte maw…óe"
  24,12,"Ko haanunoo tuma nde nanu…óon …óum, wor…ìe gom…óin…ìe …ìen e rew…ìe gom…óin…ìe …ìen …ìe yananee ka wonkiiji ma…ì…ìe ko mo∆¥∆¥i, …ìe wi'a: \"∆äum ko penaale …ìanngu…óe nii"
  24,13,"Ko haanunoo ko nde …ìe addata e …óum seedee…ìe nayo, si …ìe addaali seedee…ìe …ìen; haray …ìen …óon, ka Alla ko kam…ìe woni fenoo…ìe …ìen"
